[2018/09/19 04:25:24] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;
[2018/09/19 04:25:24] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

        FROM mfo_usuario_plan up, mfo_plan p
        WHERE p.id_plan = up.id_plan 
        AND ((up.estado = 1)||(up.estado = 0 AND up.id_comprobante <> ''))
        AND up.id_usuario = 7 ORDER BY fecha_compra ASC
[2018/09/19 04:27:39] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan

    AND r.id_requisitoOferta = o.id_requisitoOferta

      r.edad_minima, r.licencia, r.viajar, u.nombres AS empresa, u.id_usuario FROM mfo_oferta o, mfo_usuario u, mfo_requisitooferta r, mfo_escolaridad e, mfo_area a, mfo_nivelinteres n, mfo_jornada j, mfo_ciudad c, mfo_provincia p WHERE o.estado = 1

    AND e.id_escolaridad = o.id_escolaridad

    AND p.id_provincia = c.id_provincia

    AND a.id_area = o.id_area
    AND n.id_nivelInteres = o.id_nivelInteres

    AND a.id_area = o.id_area

    GROUP BY o.id_ofertas;

        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1

        FROM mfo_permisoplan p

        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2

        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

[2018/09/20 02:10:51] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo,

        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2

        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

        FROM mfo_permisoplan p

[2018/09/20 02:33:23] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, up.id_comprobante, up.fecha_compra, if(up.num_post_rest <> '',num_post_rest,'-') as num_post_rest, if(up.fecha_caducidad <> '',fecha_caducidad,'Infinito') as fecha_caducidad, up.id_usuario_plan, up.estado
        FROM mfo_usuario_plan up, mfo_plan p
        WHERE p.id_plan = up.id_plan 
        AND ((up.estado = 1)||(up.estado = 0 AND up.id_comprobante <> ''))
        AND up.id_usuario = 5 ORDER BY fecha_compra ASC
[2018/09/20 02:33:23] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

        FROM mfo_permisoplan p

        FROM mfo_permisoplan p

[2018/09/20 02:55:57] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

        AND t.id_sucursal = 1

        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;
[2018/09/20 06:13:57] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;
